title: New Creator: DJ John Askew
body:
Name: John Askew

Socials: https://twitter.com/djjohnaskew
https://www.facebook.com/djjohnaskew/
https://www.instagram.com/djjohnaskew/

Info: 
DJ John Askew, label boss of VII, is a tech/trance producer/dj from The UK. After the huge success of his debut single “Vellum” in 2001, he has delivered release after release of consistently high quality club music - either through his own Discover label or via one of his many remixes for high profile labels such as Duty Free, Ministry of Sound, Euphonic and Paul van Dyk’s legendary Vandit. 
From guest appearances on BBC Radio One, to hosting his own show on London’s prestigious Kiss 100, from exclusive residencies at 3 of the World’s most influential clubs (The Gallery, Cream and Ministry of Sound) to an ever increasing diary of guest slots around the world, Askew is plugged in.

Launch - $ASKEW will be distributed to current fans that share his announcement, as well as a reward for purchasers of his forthcoming single release early April.
Holding - $ASKEW holders will have access to a monthly collectibles raffle that will begin with just physical items, and graduate to NFTs over time.
Transaction - $ASKEW will be used for ticketed events, merchandise, and song feedback sessions.

Treasury: $1000

A 'yes' will approve this prop and a $1000 gift coin grant.
A 'no" will deny $ASKEW.
